PERSONA <- subset(AIRBNB, room_type == "Entire home/apt") %>% group_by(N_group) %>% summarize(N = n()) %>% mutate(pct = N/sum(N))


##CREAMOS VARIABLE BOOLEAN UNO O MÃS DE UNO

PERSONA[2:4, "uno"] <- "MÃ¡s de uno"
